{
  "stem": "17426.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 88.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you imagine how I felt, when the first drops of water fell on my head, and I stuck my tongue out, and I saw it was water?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a new life again, even in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Life was so precious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't want to lose it, not in this god forsaken place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we found Joe in the showers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, the three of us, did-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] made up our mind to stay close to one another.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when they will partition off groups to here and there, we would stay together possibly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we got-- when we were tattooed with numbers on our arm--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The number is 141129.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father's number, we kept him in the middle, was 141130.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother's number was 141131.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was in back, I was in front, and my father in the middle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We were given the same zebra style, zebra stripe uniforms, as we have seen the others wear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were brought into a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what was called a [GERMAN], death block.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why that block, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was a quarantine block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If any one of us would have had typhoid or any kind of infectious disease, we would all go to the chimney.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Fortunately, no one did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so after three weeks or so, IG farm people came and picked us to work in Auschwitz III, which was Buna, in an [INAUDIBLE] camp of Auschwitz III, by the name of Furstengrube.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was this main camp, the Stammlager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was Auschwitz main camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
